[0m[49m[39m  162, 164[0m:[39m[49m flowchart TD
[0m[49m[39m  163, 165[0m:[39m[49m     A[EHR Data\nLabs, Meds, Imaging, Toxicity] -->|Glue ETL| B[S3 Data Lake\nTrajectory Dataset]
[0m[49m[39m  164, 166[0m:[39m[49m     B --> C[SageMaker Training\nOffline RL - CQL/BCQ]
