[0m[49m[39m  558, 585[0m:[39m[49m **Performance benchmarks (from retrospective evaluation):**
[0m[49m[39m  559, 586[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  560, 587[0m:[39m[49m | Metric | Typical Value |
